<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06069c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06069c">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06069c"> 69(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> tomcat whiskers amuse / tail laugh / Miss</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Conte moral &agrave; dessiner et &agrave; narrer. &mdash; Le CHAT NOIR et la SOURIS GRISE, le BOL DE CR&Egrave;ME et l&apos;ESCALIER. C&apos;est tr&egrave;s net, la donn&eacute;e pr&eacute;sentant d&apos;abord les &ecirc;tres anim&eacute;s et laissant au second plan les &ecirc;tres sans mouvement. Sur un vaste <i>tableau noir</i> encadr&eacute; d&apos;une vignette form&eacute;e de feuilles de ch&acirc;taigniers <i>dessin&eacute;es en craies ocre et brune</i> d&apos;apr&egrave;s la branche plac&eacute;e en fronton, <mark>Miss</mark> trace six lignes horizontales et dessine sur la premi&egrave;re du haut la silhouette de Minet. <mark>Sa longue queue fait rire</mark> les petits et sa belle <mark>moustache les amuse</mark>. Au milieu de l&apos;escalier se trouve un bol de cr&egrave;me que Miss a t&ocirc;t fait de dessiner ainsi que la petite souris qui appara&icirc;t sous la derni&egrave;re marche. <font color="green">[Moral tale to draw and narrate. &mdash; The BLACK CAT and the GRAY MOUSE, the CREAM BOWL and the STAIRCASE. It is very clear, the data presenting animated beings first and leaving in the background the beings without movement. On a large blackboard framed by a vignette made of chestnut leaves drawn in ocher and brown chalks after the branch placed on the pediment, Miss draws six horizontal lines and draws on the first of the top the silhouette of Minet. His long tail makes the little ones laugh and his beautiful mustache amuses them. In the middle of the stairs is a bowl of cream that Miss was quick to draw and the little mouse that appears under the last step.]</font> <small> ?. ?, <a name="LARA" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#LARA"><cite title="source">La Revue Philantropique</cite></a> (????) 235-6</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
